<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Can NFTs on Polygon Be Used for More Than Just Collectibles and Digital Art, Such as Real-World Asset Tokenization?</h3>



<p>Yes, NFTs on Polygon can be used for real-world asset tokenization, including property, collectibles, and more. This provides a unique opportunity for ownership representation and facilitates fractional ownership and trading of physical assets.</p>



<h3 class="wp-block-heading">What Are the Potential Legal and Copyright Issues That Creators and Buyers Should Be Aware of When Using Polygon NFT Marketplaces?</h3>



<p>When using Polygon NFT marketplaces, creators and buyers should be aware of potential legal and copyright issues. Ensure you understand licensing rights, intellectual property laws, and the implications of tokenizing digital assets to protect yourself legally.</p>



